# Nx/EXLA benchmarking

```elixir
Mix.install([
  {:nx, "~> 0.2.0"},
  {:exla, "~> 0.2.0"},
  {:benchee, "~> 1.0"}
])

Nx.default_backend(EXLA.Backend)
Nx.Defn.global_default_options(compiler: EXLA)
```

